 350:Lib/StdPeriphs/src/stm32f4xx_rcc.c **** /**
 351:Lib/StdPeriphs/src/stm32f4xx_rcc.c ****   * @brief  Enables or disables the Internal High Speed oscillator (HSI).
 352:Lib/StdPeriphs/src/stm32f4xx_rcc.c ****   * @note   The HSI is stopped by hardware when entering STOP and STANDBY modes.
 353:Lib/StdPeriphs/src/stm32f4xx_rcc.c ****   *         It is used (enabled by hardware) as system clock source after startup
 354:Lib/StdPeriphs/src/stm32f4xx_rcc.c ****   *         from Reset, wakeup from STOP and STANDBY mode, or in case of failure
 355:Lib/StdPeriphs/src/stm32f4xx_rcc.c ****   *         of the HSE used directly or indirectly as system clock (if the Clock
 356:Lib/StdPeriphs/src/stm32f4xx_rcc.c ****   *         Security System CSS is enabled).             
