 934:Lib/StdPeriphs/src/stm32f4xx_rcc.c ****   *            @arg RCC_MCO2Div_2: division by 2 applied to MCO2 clock
 935:Lib/StdPeriphs/src/stm32f4xx_rcc.c ****   *            @arg RCC_MCO2Div_3: division by 3 applied to MCO2 clock
 936:Lib/StdPeriphs/src/stm32f4xx_rcc.c ****   *            @arg RCC_MCO2Div_4: division by 4 applied to MCO2 clock
 937:Lib/StdPeriphs/src/stm32f4xx_rcc.c ****   *            @arg RCC_MCO2Div_5: division by 5 applied to MCO2 clock
 938:Lib/StdPeriphs/src/stm32f4xx_rcc.c ****   * @note  For STM32F410xx devices to output I2SCLK clock on MCO2 you should have
