 969:Lib/StdPeriphs/src/stm32f4xx_rcc.c **** 
 970:Lib/StdPeriphs/src/stm32f4xx_rcc.c **** /** @defgroup RCC_Group2 System AHB and APB busses clocks configuration functions
 971:Lib/StdPeriphs/src/stm32f4xx_rcc.c ****  *  @brief   System, AHB and APB busses clocks configuration functions
 972:Lib/StdPeriphs/src/stm32f4xx_rcc.c ****  *
 973:Lib/StdPeriphs/src/stm32f4xx_rcc.c **** @verbatim   
 974:Lib/StdPeriphs/src/stm32f4xx_rcc.c ****  ===============================================================================
 975:Lib/StdPeriphs/src/stm32f4xx_rcc.c ****       ##### System, AHB and APB busses clocks configuration functions #####
 976:Lib/StdPeriphs/src/stm32f4xx_rcc.c ****  ===============================================================================  
 977:Lib/StdPeriphs/src/stm32f4xx_rcc.c ****     [..]
 978:Lib/StdPeriphs/src/stm32f4xx_rcc.c ****       This section provide functions allowing to configure the System, AHB, APB1 and 
 979:Lib/StdPeriphs/src/stm32f4xx_rcc.c ****       APB2 busses clocks.
 980:Lib/StdPeriphs/src/stm32f4xx_rcc.c ****   
 981:Lib/StdPeriphs/src/stm32f4xx_rcc.c ****       (#) Several clock sources can be used to drive the System clock (SYSCLK): HSI,
 982:Lib/StdPeriphs/src/stm32f4xx_rcc.c ****           HSE and PLL.
 983:Lib/StdPeriphs/src/stm32f4xx_rcc.c ****           The AHB clock (HCLK) is derived from System clock through configurable 
 984:Lib/StdPeriphs/src/stm32f4xx_rcc.c ****           prescaler and used to clock the CPU, memory and peripherals mapped 
 985:Lib/StdPeriphs/src/stm32f4xx_rcc.c ****           on AHB bus (DMA, GPIO...). APB1 (PCLK1) and APB2 (PCLK2) clocks are derived 
 986:Lib/StdPeriphs/src/stm32f4xx_rcc.c ****           from AHB clock through configurable prescalers and used to clock 
 987:Lib/StdPeriphs/src/stm32f4xx_rcc.c ****           the peripherals mapped on these busses. You can use 
 988:Lib/StdPeriphs/src/stm32f4xx_rcc.c ****           "RCC_GetClocksFreq()" function to retrieve the frequencies of these clocks.  
 989:Lib/StdPeriphs/src/stm32f4xx_rcc.c **** 
 990:Lib/StdPeriphs/src/stm32f4xx_rcc.c ****       -@- All the peripheral clocks are derived from the System clock (SYSCLK) except:
 991:Lib/StdPeriphs/src/stm32f4xx_rcc.c ****         (+@) I2S: the I2S clock can be derived either from a specific PLL (PLLI2S) or
 992:Lib/StdPeriphs/src/stm32f4xx_rcc.c ****              from an external clock mapped on the I2S_CKIN pin. 
 993:Lib/StdPeriphs/src/stm32f4xx_rcc.c ****              You have to use RCC_I2SCLKConfig() function to configure this clock. 
 994:Lib/StdPeriphs/src/stm32f4xx_rcc.c ****         (+@) RTC: the RTC clock can be derived either from the LSI, LSE or HSE clock
 995:Lib/StdPeriphs/src/stm32f4xx_rcc.c ****              divided by 2 to 31. You have to use RCC_RTCCLKConfig() and RCC_RTCCLKCmd()
 996:Lib/StdPeriphs/src/stm32f4xx_rcc.c ****              functions to configure this clock. 
 997:Lib/StdPeriphs/src/stm32f4xx_rcc.c ****         (+@) USB OTG FS, SDIO and RTC: USB OTG FS require a frequency equal to 48 MHz
 998:Lib/StdPeriphs/src/stm32f4xx_rcc.c ****              to work correctly, while the SDIO require a frequency equal or lower than
 999:Lib/StdPeriphs/src/stm32f4xx_rcc.c ****              to 48. This clock is derived of the main PLL through PLLQ divider.
1000:Lib/StdPeriphs/src/stm32f4xx_rcc.c ****         (+@) IWDG clock which is always the LSI clock.
1001:Lib/StdPeriphs/src/stm32f4xx_rcc.c ****        
1002:Lib/StdPeriphs/src/stm32f4xx_rcc.c ****       (#) For STM32F405xx/407xx and STM32F415xx/417xx devices, the maximum frequency 
1003:Lib/StdPeriphs/src/stm32f4xx_rcc.c ****          of the SYSCLK and HCLK is 168 MHz, PCLK2 84 MHz and PCLK1 42 MHz. Depending 
1004:Lib/StdPeriphs/src/stm32f4xx_rcc.c ****          on the device voltage range, the maximum frequency should be adapted accordingly:
1005:Lib/StdPeriphs/src/stm32f4xx_rcc.c ****  +-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
1006:Lib/StdPeriphs/src/stm32f4xx_rcc.c ****  | Latency       |                HCLK clock frequency (MHz)                           |
1007:Lib/StdPeriphs/src/stm32f4xx_rcc.c ****  |               |---------------------------------------------------------------------|
1008:Lib/StdPeriphs/src/stm32f4xx_rcc.c ****  |               | voltage range  | voltage range  | voltage range   | voltage range   |
1009:Lib/StdPeriphs/src/stm32f4xx_rcc.c ****  |               | 2.7 V - 3.6 V  | 2.4 V - 2.7 V  | 2.1 V - 2.4 V   | 1.8 V - 2.1 V   |
1010:Lib/StdPeriphs/src/stm32f4xx_rcc.c ****  |---------------|----------------|----------------|-----------------|-----------------|
1011:Lib/StdPeriphs/src/stm32f4xx_rcc.c ****  |0WS(1CPU cycle)|0 < HCLK <= 30  |0 < HCLK <= 24  |0 < HCLK <= 22   |0 < HCLK <= 20   |
1012:Lib/StdPeriphs/src/stm32f4xx_rcc.c ****  |---------------|----------------|----------------|-----------------|-----------------|
