1277:Lib/StdPeriphs/src/stm32f4xx_rcc.c **** /**
1278:Lib/StdPeriphs/src/stm32f4xx_rcc.c ****   * @brief  Returns the frequencies of different on chip clocks; SYSCLK, HCLK, 
1279:Lib/StdPeriphs/src/stm32f4xx_rcc.c ****   *         PCLK1 and PCLK2.
1280:Lib/StdPeriphs/src/stm32f4xx_rcc.c ****   * 
1281:Lib/StdPeriphs/src/stm32f4xx_rcc.c ****   * @note   The system frequency computed by this function is not the real 
1282:Lib/StdPeriphs/src/stm32f4xx_rcc.c ****   *         frequency in the chip. It is calculated based on the predefined 
1283:Lib/StdPeriphs/src/stm32f4xx_rcc.c ****   *         constant and the selected clock source:
1284:Lib/StdPeriphs/src/stm32f4xx_rcc.c ****   * @note     If SYSCLK source is HSI, function returns values based on HSI_VALUE(*)
ARM GAS  C:\Users\asus\AppData\Local\Temp\ccEdY3aN.s 			page 37


1285:Lib/StdPeriphs/src/stm32f4xx_rcc.c ****   * @note     If SYSCLK source is HSE, function returns values based on HSE_VALUE(**)
1286:Lib/StdPeriphs/src/stm32f4xx_rcc.c ****   * @note     If SYSCLK source is PLL, function returns values based on HSE_VALUE(**) 
1287:Lib/StdPeriphs/src/stm32f4xx_rcc.c ****   *           or HSI_VALUE(*) multiplied/divided by the PLL factors.         
1288:Lib/StdPeriphs/src/stm32f4xx_rcc.c ****   * @note     (*) HSI_VALUE is a constant defined in stm32f4xx.h file (default value
1289:Lib/StdPeriphs/src/stm32f4xx_rcc.c ****   *               16 MHz) but the real value may vary depending on the variations
1290:Lib/StdPeriphs/src/stm32f4xx_rcc.c ****   *               in voltage and temperature.
1291:Lib/StdPeriphs/src/stm32f4xx_rcc.c ****   * @note     (**) HSE_VALUE is a constant defined in stm32f4xx.h file (default value
1292:Lib/StdPeriphs/src/stm32f4xx_rcc.c ****   *                25 MHz), user has to ensure that HSE_VALUE is same as the real
1293:Lib/StdPeriphs/src/stm32f4xx_rcc.c ****   *                frequency of the crystal used. Otherwise, this function may
1294:Lib/StdPeriphs/src/stm32f4xx_rcc.c ****   *                have wrong result.
1295:Lib/StdPeriphs/src/stm32f4xx_rcc.c ****   *                
1296:Lib/StdPeriphs/src/stm32f4xx_rcc.c ****   * @note   The result of this function could be not correct when using fractional
1297:Lib/StdPeriphs/src/stm32f4xx_rcc.c ****   *         value for HSE crystal.
1298:Lib/StdPeriphs/src/stm32f4xx_rcc.c ****   *   
1299:Lib/StdPeriphs/src/stm32f4xx_rcc.c ****   * @param  RCC_Clocks: pointer to a RCC_ClocksTypeDef structure which will hold
1300:Lib/StdPeriphs/src/stm32f4xx_rcc.c ****   *          the clocks frequencies.
1301:Lib/StdPeriphs/src/stm32f4xx_rcc.c ****   *     
1302:Lib/StdPeriphs/src/stm32f4xx_rcc.c ****   * @note   This function can be used by the user application to compute the 
1303:Lib/StdPeriphs/src/stm32f4xx_rcc.c ****   *         baudrate for the communication peripherals or configure other parameters.
1304:Lib/StdPeriphs/src/stm32f4xx_rcc.c ****   * @note   Each time SYSCLK, HCLK, PCLK1 and/or PCLK2 clock changes, this function
1305:Lib/StdPeriphs/src/stm32f4xx_rcc.c ****   *         must be called to update the structure's field. Otherwise, any
1306:Lib/StdPeriphs/src/stm32f4xx_rcc.c ****   *         configuration based on this function will be incorrect.
1307:Lib/StdPeriphs/src/stm32f4xx_rcc.c ****   *    
1308:Lib/StdPeriphs/src/stm32f4xx_rcc.c ****   * @retval None
1309:Lib/StdPeriphs/src/stm32f4xx_rcc.c ****   */
